summary:
This is mainly based on the assumption that Tyrion will betray Daenerys. 
I wholly believe in the whole “only death pays for...
body:
Expectation vs Reality

This is mainly based on the assumption that Tyrion will betray Daenerys.


I wholly believe in the whole “only death pays for life”. Viserion dying means Dany can have a baby. And since Viserion was the white dragon, I believe our little targling will have silver hair. The only way I see a second/dark haired baby being born is if Drogon dies. Yes Rhaegal, there are no green haired babies. You got lucky.


I don’t see any more direwolves making an appearance except for the true Starks. Only ghost will remain. And if I’m being honest, the only two direwolves left alive are Nymeria and Ghost. Which means that it’s high unlikely for the direwolf species to make a comeback with only two of the species left.
